{"product_id":"copy-of-organic-body-wash-250ml-1","title":"Vielö Organic Body Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic body wash, specially designed to cleanse, nourish and moisturise dry and sensitive skin gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat protein (moisturising), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of arnica (soothing), birch leaf (purifying) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to wet skin. Leave on briefly. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv d