Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Xanthan Gum*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Gluten*, Citronellol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Betula Alba Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (68,3%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091841130823,"sku":null,"price":27.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-wash-250ml-637632.jpg?v=1739897340","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/copy-of-organic-body-wash-250ml-1","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}